UUTrack.Model.config module¶

UUTrack.Model.workerSaver module¶

UUTrack.Model.workerSaver.workerSaver(fileData, meta, q)[source]¶

Function that can be run in a separate thread for continuously save data to disk. fileData – STRING with the path to the file to use. meta – A string with metadata. It is kept as a string in order to provide flexibility for other programs. q – Queue that will store all the images to be saved to disk.
